#About the box
The Box included ubuntu-14.04 and hadoop 2.7.1
When vagrant is up in first time, it automatically download hadoop and install it.
The Box automatically create user/vagrant directory on hdfs, it starts hdfs and yarn on bootstrapping.
Happy using.

#Installation of box
vagrant init girginsoft/ubuntu-hadoop; vagrant up --provider virtualbox

#Box Url
https://atlas.hashicorp.com/girginsoft/boxes/ubuntu-hadoop
